This is the final episode before the end. Here we descend into 50% madness and 50% memes, and it is up to us to discover which is which

1 RT = 1 conspiracy

1. Synchronicity following

The idea that you can follow the synchronicites you encounter and go deeper and deeper until you somehow are able to "break away from the Matrix". The more synchornicities you discover, the weirder the world around you will start to become.

2. Protodeities

The belief that some creatures are able to ascend into the status of godhood, and that omnipotence is not something that can not be acquired. Some great warriors or emperors in the forgotten past managed to ascend above mere humanity and into the divine.
Soundcloud

3. No Heaven, only Hell

A thought experiment, imagining a cruel Demiurge, who has crafted our world with the purpose of some abstract torture. No matter what we do, we end up in endless pain.

Of course, this is not true, do not worry about it.

4. Spongebob Defecation 

Allegedly, in some part of Brazil, an episode of Spongebob containing an added special sound was played.

This sound was the infamous hypothetical "brown wave" that causes humans to shit themselves upon hearing it. Hundreds of kiddos did exactly that.

You can see how the above could be highly useful in war to stop an incoming group of soldiers, or to demoralize the enemy and cause infections. Imagine this sound played by Civil defense siren speakers in New York, London...

6. Endless Elevators

There is a famous Korean urban legend, talking about getting into an elevator in a 15-story building and pressing a specific sequence of buttons, which will lead you into a "secret" floor in another dimension. If you fail, you are trapped in an elevator maze

7. Bugchasing

This one, as I sadly am able to confirm, is not a conspiracy. There exist groups of AIDS-infected men (this is mostly a homosexual community phenomenon) that willingly infect others with AIDS by having sex with them without telling about their disease. Disturbing!

In some more serious (read: psychopathic) cases, rape is involved. There are also groups for people looking to be infected with AIDS, most often because they want to "participate" in this too.

As disgusting as this sounds, it is nothing compared to some stuff I've read about...
